Package org.jungrapht.visualization.layout.algorithms

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IterativeLayoutAlgorithm<V>
    A LayoutAlgorithm that may utilize a pre-relax phase, which is a loop of calls to step that occurr in the current thread instead of in a new Thread.
    LayoutAlgorithm<V>
    LayoutAlgorithm is a visitor to the LayoutModel.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractIterativeLayoutAlgorithm<V>
    For Iterative algorithms that perform delayed operations on a Thread, save off the layoutModel so that it can be accessed by the threaded code.
    AbstractIterativeLayoutAlgorithm.Builder<V,T extends AbstractIterativeLayoutAlgorithm<V>,B extends AbstractIterativeLayoutAlgorithm.Builder<V,T,B>>  
    AnimationLayoutAlgorithm<V>  
    AnimationLayoutAlgorithm.Builder<V>  
    BalloonLayoutAlgorithm<V>
    A Layout implementation that assigns positions to Tree or Graph vertices using associations with nested circles ("balloons").
    BalloonLayoutAlgorithm.Builder<V,T extends BalloonLayoutAlgorithm<V>,B extends BalloonLayoutAlgorithm.Builder<V,T,B>>  
    CircleLayoutAlgorithm<V>
    A Layout implementation that positions vertices equally spaced on a regular circle.
    CircleLayoutAlgorithm.Builder<V>  
    DAGLayoutAlgorithm<V>
    An implementation of Layout suitable for tree-like directed acyclic graphs.
    DAGLayoutAlgorithm.Builder<V>  
    EdgePredicatedTreeLayoutAlgorithm<V,E>  
    EdgePredicatedTreeLayoutAlgorithm.Builder<V,E>  
    EdgeSortingTreeLayoutAlgorithm<V,E>
    An extension of TreeLayoutAlgorithm that allows a Comparator<E> for edges so that the children of each vertex are accessed in a supplied order.
    EdgeSortingTreeLayoutAlgorithm.Builder<V,E,T extends EdgeSortingTreeLayoutAlgorithm<V,E>,B extends EdgeSortingTreeLayoutAlgorithm.Builder<V,E,T,B>>
    a builder to create an instance of a EdgeSortingTreeLayoutAlgorithm.
    FRLayoutAlgorithm<V>
    Implements the Fruchterman-Reingold force-directed algorithm for vertex layout.
    FRLayoutAlgorithm.Builder<V>  
    ISOMLayoutAlgorithm<V>
    Implements a self-organizing map layout algorithm, based on Meyer's self-organizing graph methods.
    ISOMLayoutAlgorithm.Builder<V>  
    KKLayoutAlgorithm<V>
